      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system providing a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Recent service includes a valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain integrity and lateral dynamics remain sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
